00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:59,380
我们破译了一段匿名密码
Code was broken on an anonymous transmission.

189
00:13:01,290 --> 00:13:03,060
出自政府内部
It was internal.

190
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:05,530
所以不能让政府部门参与破案
We can't go to the usual agencies.

191
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:08,460
敌人已经打入内部
The government itself has been penetrated.

192
00:13:08,570 --> 00:13:14,030
这段时间，总统 要参加3项公开活动
The President has three public engagements during that time.

193
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:18,630
