真漂亮
This is beautiful.

243
00:15:59,970 --> 00:16:02,700
这电话二十四小时都有人接听
Someone will be at this number night or day.

244
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:10,510
看到他刚才做什么了吗？ 他才不是在拍发动机
You see what he did? He didn't need a photo of the engine.

