Yeah, I think he better worry.

259
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:33,950
它不会有事
Yeah, he'll be fine.

260
00:18:35,130 --> 00:18:39,080
每天喂它一次 孤独时给它念念弹道表就没事了
Just feed him once a day. Read him a few ballistics tables if he looks lonely.

261
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,460
好，再见
Yep. I'm out.

262
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:43,700
老朋友
Come here, buddy.

263
00:18:44,470 --> 00:18:45,630
好了
Okay.

264
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:49,790
我出几天门你不会寂寞吧？
Think you'll be able to tough it out without me for a couple days?

265
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,610
那好
Yeah.

